(ns gis-client.core
  (:require [reagent.core :as rc]
            [reagent.dom :as rd ]
            ["@blueprintjs/core" :as bpc]))

(defonce app-state (atom {:text "Hello world!"}))

(defn root-component []
  [:div
   [:h1 (:text @app-state)]
   [:h3 "Edit this, and watch it change!"]
    [:> bpc/Button {:icon "eye-open" :text "Log to Console!" :onClick #(js/console.log "logged to console")}]])

(defn render ;; metadata (^:dev/after-load) shadow-cljs lifecycle hook run after hot-reload, runs reloaded code
  "rendering of components"
  []
  (rd/render [root-component] (js/document.getElementById "root"))
  (js/console.log "--- reloaded components ---"))

(defn ^:export init ;; metadata (^:export) prepends "export" to javascript compiler
  "initial loading of system" 
  []  
  (render)
  (js/console.log "--- initiated system ---"))

(comment
  (start))
